\begin_inset Formula $y_{i}$
\end_inset

 can be defined as a generalised GC method 
\begin_inset Formula $x\rightarrow y_{i}|(y_{1},y_{2},...,y_{i-1},y_{i+1},...,y_{n}).$
\end_inset

